data.description: Motivated Seller! This fantastic 4-bedroom, 2-full bathroom ranch is nestled in the picturesque Oldham County. As you enter through the front door you will notice how spacious it is with vaulted ceilings and an open floor plan. The wide-open kitchen has granite countertops, a sizable floating island, white-painted cabinets, and stainless-steel appliances. There is a large dining room and an enormous living room with a beautiful gas push-button fireplace. The laminate wood floors are throughout the entire house. The 2-car attached garage has additional storage. As you walk out back there is plenty of entertainment space on the large covered rear porch. Convenient to award-winning Oldham County schools and Glen Eagles golf course is just across the street. Schedule your private showing!
